Mantle nodded. "We use all sorts of nano stuff. This is a very experimental 
ship, although it is one of the best. There is a very large supply of 
nanobots on the ship, and they can make more. They're like an extension to 
Cyndro's mind. Cyndro is our ship's mind. He's like another bot, but with 
quite alot more intelligence, thought capacity, and reasoning skills. He can 
control every function of the ship, and its much better to have a smart mind 
controlling it than a machine. What I plan to do is have the nanobots go 
through underground and take the Cybertronian Fire apart from the inside, 
and add the pieces onto the Element. We can have alot of the city done by 
the time the battle's over."
